  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Newspaper advertisement</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1929</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The Belgrade ‘Kolarac’ cinema advertises the melodrama ‘Erotikon’ starring Ita Rina in Serbian Cyrillic letters. The leaflet is framed with simple lines.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The text translates as: ‘Kolarac organizes a grand premiere, which is also the international premiere of the great Czech film Erotikon. Starring: Ita Rina (Ida Kravanja), Olaf Fjord, Luigi Serventi. Director: Gustav Machatý. Monopoly: Kolarac – Warner Bros. Miss Ita Rina will be personally present at the grand premiere tomorrow. Seats are numbered. Advance booking from 11–12 and a half and [sic!] from 7 in the afternoon. For tomorrow, no reduction will be granted’.</ab>
